~ Testing behavioral inconsistencies and edge cases

~ EDGE 1: What does split return for empty string?
show split("", ",")

~ EDGE 2: What does split return when separator not found?
show split("hello", "x")

~ EDGE 3: What does index_of return for empty string in empty string?
show index_of("", "")

~ EDGE 4: Replace with empty string?
show replace("hello", "l", "")

~ EDGE 5: Join on empty list
show join([], ", ")

~ EDGE 6: Starts/ends_with empty?
show starts_with("hello", "")
show ends_with("hello", "")

~ EDGE 7: trim behavior on already trimmed
show trim("hello")
show trim("  hello  ")

~ EDGE 8: split with separator == text?
show split("hello", "hello")

~ EDGE 9: index_of with empty needle
show index_of("hello", "")

~ EDGE 10: sort empty list
show sort([])

